Do we need to go to the hospital

00:17:35.500 --> 00:17:36.340
for a CT scan?

00:17:36.760 --> 00:17:37.100
Grandpa,

00:17:37.860 --> 00:17:38.680
look me in the eyes.

00:17:41.520 --> 00:17:43.580
It's okay, I'm fine now.

