I'll give Grandpa

00:17:52.480 --> 00:17:53.300
a quick check-up.

00:17:53.900 --> 00:17:54.520
Okay,

00:17:54.720 --> 00:17:55.340
come on in.

00:17:55.360 --> 00:17:55.700
Alright.

00:17:56.400 --> 00:17:56.680
Come on.

00:17:57.280 --> 00:17:57.680
Easy.

