Exactly, Grandpa.

00:20:33.820 --> 00:20:35.260
If you'd gone to the hospital sooner

00:20:35.280 --> 00:20:36.180
to get this fixed,

00:20:36.180 --> 00:20:36.820
you wouldn't have had to

00:20:36.820 --> 00:20:37.760
suffer so much.

