Will it come back?

00:20:39.700 --> 00:20:40.120
It might.

00:20:41.140 --> 00:20:41.780
So Grandpa,

00:20:42.120 --> 00:20:42.880
get plenty of rest,

00:20:42.940 --> 00:20:43.540
but try to stay active.

